metadata.title: Sparkle and Bash 36-Pack Small Red Party Favor Bags, 5.5x3.2x9-Inch Paper Goodie Bags with Stickers for Birthday Party Supplies (6 Designs)
features: Red Treat Bags for Kids: Use this set of small red bags as a convenient wrapping solution for gifts and presents for a birthday, holidays, or graduation parties
Customizable: Decorate the red party goodie bags with the included stickers, or customize with your own name tags or photos; make custom bags full of candy, cookies, dolls, and toys (not included)
Reliable Quality: The red paper bags are made from high-quality 120gsm kraft paper
The Perfect Size: The small paper gift bags each measure 5.5 x 9 x 3.15 inches
Comes With: You will receive 36 small paper red bags with 1 sheet of 36 stickers
description: Our set of 36 red paper bags offers a quick and easy packaging solution for special occasions including an upcoming baby shower, Christmas party, New Year, or birthday party; you can also use the small paper bags for small business and bakery packaging. Decorate the red gift bags with the included red stickers or create custom name tags. Each of the red party goodie bags with handles measures 5.5 x 9 x 3.15 inches, perfectly sized to hold small gifts, party favors, prizes, jewelry, and merchandise (not included).
